Create new IPv4Prefix subobject

Parameters:
loose - true if hop is loos, false if hop is strict
tlvLength - length of this subobject including length and type fields
ip - IPv4 address in this subobject
ipv4Length - length of the IPv4 address
padding - padding bits usually set to 0
